{"tid":1940884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"YSL巴黎世家Gucci轉製口罩","createTime":"2020-03-24T05:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T06:59:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e74aad74e680473a5dae51a0b1f54d40d31b44de","tid":1940884,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:25:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200324/HI6HSV6CMCHUSQC42HTFWPWLHU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200324%2FHI6HSV6CMCHUSQC42HTFWPWLHU%2F&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1kuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=fdecad84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200324%2FHI6HSV6CMCHUSQC42HTFWPWLHU%2F&h=5cf4e6a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200324/HI6HSV6CMCHUSQC42HTFWPWLHU/</a><br />\n<br />\nYSL巴黎世家Gucci轉製口罩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200324/large/1584976671_2204.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200324%2Flarge%2F1584976671_2204.gif&h=c4eee641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n意大利全國封城下彌撒要轉網上直播，神父對着貼上教友自拍照的空長凳講道。<br />\n<br />\n疫情引發口罩荒，法國和意大利有高檔時裝品牌擬大量生產口罩和消毒搓手液，並從中國搜購口罩捐贈給當地政府。大馬則將從國外搜購口罩，向國民免費派發。土耳其則強制口罩廠向政府出售口罩，否則充公。<br />\n<br />\n法國高檔時裝品牌YSL和巴黎世家的母公司開雲集團宣佈，兩個品牌將會投身製造口罩之列，又指會將預計從中國購入的300萬片醫療口罩捐給法國醫護人員；旗下另一時裝品牌Gucci亦會製造110萬片口罩，連同5.5萬件防護衣捐贈給意大利；並已捐款支持法國巴斯德研究院研究新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n同屬奢侈品牌的LV則指，已聯同法國政府向中國供應商搜購4,000萬片口罩，並已將部份香水生產線改作生產消毒搓手液，捐贈給法國政府。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大馬國外搜購免費派發<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：酒吧轟不公：食飯唔會播毒？<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞首相慕尤丁宣佈，將從國外購入1,000萬片口罩，免費派發給有需要人士，並撥款7.8億令吉（13.72億港元）增聘醫護人手和購買醫療物資抗疫。當地錄得逾1,500宗確診個案，14人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其政府則要求口罩廠停止囤貨，並在日內與衞生部簽約售出，否則將全數充公。當地錄得1,256宗確診個案，30人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/中央社"},{"pid":"8002639a4ea62d3ebd92623bffdcff0cbbd350a6","tid":1940884,"uid":132287,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:31:35.000Z","msg":"D口罩印個logo<br />\n每個賣3000$"},{"pid":"d066088b841c986d41dc8e98f3458872d7ceba0c","tid":1940884,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:36:24.000Z","msg":"我以為不嬲都有㖭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://augustinewong.files.wordpress.com/2009/05/lv-mask1.jpg?w=584\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faugustinewong.files.wordpress.com%2F2009%2F05%2Flv-mask1.jpg%3Fw%3D584&h=c09b9251&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25f3a46e22861d8b0dc6dd983d985eeed8ad8812","tid":1940884,"uid":8745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:37:11.000Z","msg":"名牌口罩"},{"pid":"31ded56e185128426915b8890f91918900149f35","tid":1940884,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d066088b841c986d41dc8e98f3458872d7ceba0c","tid":1940884,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:36:24.000Z","msg":"我以為不嬲都有㖭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://augustinewong.files.wordpress.com/2009/05/lv-mask1.jpg?w=584\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faugustinewong.files.wordpress.com%2F2009%2F05%2Flv-mask1.jpg%3Fw%3D584&h=c09b9251&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/38/9b/1c/389b1cf7163aa0966767b9dd6a940cc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F38%2F9b%2F1c%2F389b1cf7163aa0966767b9dd6a940cc9.jpg&h=568012b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09b99fb243b1a6eb7bf152cf2858d4b0ba4f1f40","tid":1940884,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"31ded56e185128426915b8890f91918900149f35","tid":1940884,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d066088b841c986d41dc8e98f3458872d7ceba0c","tid":1940884,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:36:24.000Z","msg":"我以為不嬲都有㖭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://augustinewong.files.wo